'''吡啶-4-甲醛'''是一种有机化合物，化学式为C<sub>5</sub>H<sub>4</sub>NCHO，是[[吡啶甲醛|吡啶甲醛]]的[[同分异构体|同分异构体]]之一。它是无色液体，久置后会变为黄色或棕色。它可以发生芳香醛的反应，如还原胺化和生成[[席夫碱|席夫碱]]。<ref>{{cite journal |doi=10.15227/orgsyn.090.0052|title=Enantioselective Nitroaldol (Henry) Reaction of p-Nitrobenzaldehyde and Nitromethane Using a Copper (II) Complex Derived from (R,R)-1,2-Diaminocyclohexane: (1S)-1-(4-Nitrophenyl)-2-nitroethane-1-ol|journal=Organic Syntheses|year=2013|volume=90|page=52|first1=Antoinette|last1=Chougnet|first2=Wolf-D.|last2=Woggon}}</ref>它可以和吡咯缩合，得到四吡啶基卟啉。<ref>{{cite journal |doi=10.1039/c39940002313|title=Self-Assembly of Square Multiporphyrin Arrays by Metal Ion Coordination|year=1994|last1=Drain|first1=Charles Michael|last2=Lehn|first2=Jean-Marie|journal=Journal of the Chemical Society, Chemical Communications|issue=19|page=2313}}</ref>

